                <h2 data-uuid="df03fe0830474c07850ce19040b1b706">Causes and Effects of World War II</h2>
                <p data-uuid="af012309d3b6447da04c0eaf06b4f20c"><span>Fought for many reasons, </span><span>World War II had many long</span><span>-</span><span>lasting </span><span>effects on much of the world.</span><br />
                </p>
            </article>
